<meta name="description" content="The process of European unification, its spread to the East and the Baltic countries is accompanied by the formation of a joint educational and scientific space and develop uniform criteria and standards in this area across the entire continent. This process became known as the name of the University of Bologna in the Italian city of Bologna, where such initiatives have been launched. 
 Let’s us to consider the basic principles of the Bologna process and higher education in Ukraine compliance with its requirements due to the prospect of integration into the European education and research area." />
