ion" title="Conducting student attestation and semester control" class="sf-depth-2">Student attestations</a></li><li id="main-menu-link-contentcae9d45a-6358-4af3-b6d9-cbe70bbe898f" class="sf-depth-2 sf-no-children"><a href="/en/monitoring" title="Complex monitoring of the quality of training of specialists" class="sf-depth-2">Complex monitoring</a></li><li id="main-menu-link-content1fcccd1c-2fe5-4441-8a65-849db26a66f5" class="sf-depth-2 sf-no-children"><a href="/en/education_department" title="News of education" class="sf-depth-2">News of education</a></li></ul></li><li id="main-menu-link-contentdda29401-8b0b-40a4-9f26-782795d4391e" class="sf-depth-1 menuparent"><a href="/en/science" title="Science and Innovation at KPI" class="sf-depth-1 menuparent">Science and Innovation</a><ul><li id="main-menu-link-content3d474f24-25f1-44e6-b8d6-d4be18151a73" class="sf-depth-2 sf-no-children"><a href="/en/reward" title="State Prizes" class="sf-depth-2">State Prizes</a></li><li id="main-menu-link-content2affba8f-fceb-4091-a662-c111b337619a" class="sf-depth-2 sf-no-children"><a href="/en/research" title="Directions of fundamental and applied scientific researches" class="sf-depth-2">Directions of researches</a></li><li id="main-menu-link-content2b207242-1ee2-494f-a2b6-bf4d57ca79d8" class="sf-depth-2 sf-no-children"><a href="/en/publication" title="Scientific jornals" class="sf-depth-2">Scientific publications</a></li><li id="main-menu-link-content354257ba-c70e-4da2-8cb2-62f54f255435" class="sf-depth-2 sf-no-children"><a href="/en/norma" title="Competitions for scientists and researchers" class="sf-depth-2">Competitions for scientists</a></li><li id="main-menu-link-content37b5aa10-f03c-4572-bc70-c3576ad3c04a" class="sf-depth-2 sf-no-children"><a href="/en/seminar" title="Science and science-technical events" class="sf-depth-2">Plan of science events</a></li><li id="main-menu-link-content0d31b284-45d3-40b9-8549-7bc35abeea7b" class="sf-depth-2 sf-no-children"><a href="/en/ecoino" cla